endpoint

Class ChatMessage.Param

  • java.lang.Object
    • endpoint.ChatMessage.Param
  • Enclosing class:
    ChatMessage

    public static class ChatMessage.Param
extends java.lang.Object
    This inner class exist to encapsulate all the optional parameters of a message for e.g. the users list sent by a "User List" request, or a nickname notification on connection. It has been created to get a smaller size of data packets sent: in fact, the Param class is completely optional and not necessarily needed.
